Basic stuff to interact with the ISD2100 on slim consoles + stream audio data


data.c generated with:

scripts/convert.py wavfile.wav auddata.bin

xxd -n data -i auddata.bin > source/data.c

VIEW isd1200_playspi FUNCTION FOR FORMAT+BITRATE SETTING


Start audio data with scripts/sendcmd.py (or hack up the main.c if this tcp code is utterly broken)


Credits:

Main ISD library from Balázs Triszka's PicoFlasher

https://github.com/X360Tools/PicoFlasher/
